text: William Elkins or Elkin may refer to: * William Henry Pferinger Elkins (1883-1964), Canadian soldier * William Lukens Elkins (1832-1903), American businessman * William McIntire Elkins (1882–1947), American collector of rare books and Dickensiana * William Lewis Elkin (1855-1933), American astronomer
title: William Elkins
